#: includes/Admin/options/opt_docs_assistant.php:470
msgid "(Optional) Enter a Site / Product Label below — the name of the site or product where you are pasting this embed. This tells the assistant which product the visitor is asking about so it does not confuse multiple products in one knowledge base."
